                    <dl>
                        <p class=\"\\&quot;MsoNormal\\&quot;\"> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#0000ff;font-size:10.5pt;\">任职要求</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">：</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#ff0000;font-size:10.5pt;\">&nbsp;年龄35以下，薪资面议</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#ff0000;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span> </p> <p class=\"\\&quot;MsoNormal\\&quot;\"> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">1.&nbsp;有微信，微博推广方面的1年以上经验者优先，广告、营销、市场相关专业，有1~2年互联网、APP、页游/手游推广经验、、微信营销推广经验、有活动策划经验者优先；有微信公众平台开发经验者优先；</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span> </p> <p class=\"\\&quot;MsoNormal\\&quot;\"> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">2.&nbsp;了解和热爱互联网广告、传媒行业，对其现状及发展具独到见解；熟悉互联网、熟悉各大电商平台、熟悉微信、微博、网站以及各类平台营销推广；自我驱动，乐于研究、分享同行的推广经验；</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span> </p> <p class=\"\\&quot;MsoNormal\\&quot;\"> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">3.&nbsp;有良好的文字功底，能独立完成文案的撰写，具备较强的用户行为分析能力，擅于发现社会潮流、捕捉营销机遇；</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\"><br /> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">4．拥有优秀的写作能力、沟通能力、协调能力，具备独立工作能力；具备较强的开拓热情，喜欢具有挑战的工作；具备营销策划或内容类岗位工作经验者优先；</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span> </p> <p class=\"\\&quot;MsoNormal\\&quot;\"> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">5.&nbsp;负责公司微信帐号的运营，使之成为向用户传播品牌形象的重要通道；积极主动地调用公司内外资源，达成营销目的；</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\"><br /> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">6.&nbsp;依据用户成分和相关数据规划内容体系，创作相关内容和专题，不断提升活跃和关注度；</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\"><br /> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">7.&nbsp;制定用户增长目标和达成计划，利用内容传播、微信活动、营销资源等完成目标；</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\"><br /> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">8.&nbsp;良好的表达沟通能力，有培训指导经验尤佳</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">,</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">对工作有热情有信心有耐心；认同移动互联网金融事业的价值，主动持续优化营销推广方案；</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\"><br /> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">9</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">.</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">有良好的团队合作能力，积极配合同事的工作。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\"><br /> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span> </p> <p class=\"\\&quot;MsoNormal\\&quot;\"> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#0000ff;font-size:10.5pt;\">岗位职责</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">：&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span> </p> <p class=\"\\&quot;MsoNormal\\&quot;\"> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">1.主要负责公司新媒体的运营，包括微信，微博，网站内容的更新，推广以及相关推广活动的策划；负责公司APP推广；</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\"><br /> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">2.了解行业内的相关信息，了解行业动向，及时搜集整理发布行业内最新动态。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\"><br /> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">3.提高平台粉丝的活跃度，及时与粉丝进行互动。挖掘微信微博粉丝的需求，及时整理数据进行反馈，根据粉丝的需求进行相关微信微博的内容，推广活动内容的调整。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\"><br /> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">4.紧跟微信，微博的发展趋势，深入了解社交媒体的特点和资源，探索运营模式，整理出自己的一套运营方式。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\"><br /> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">5.完成部门安排的其他工作。</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span> </p> <p class=\"\\&quot;MsoNormal\\&quot;\"> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">6.&nbsp;公司上班班制：上六休一、上班时间：朝九晚六、实习期3个月转正；</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span> </p> <p class=\"\\&quot;MsoNormal\\&quot;\"> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">7.&nbsp;工作地点：苏州</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">--</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">工业园区</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span> </p> <p class=\"\\&quot;MsoNormal\\&quot;\"> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">8.&nbsp;福利待遇：国家法定的各项福利（五险一金、法定节假日、满一年以上享受带薪年休假）；</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span> </p> <p class=\"\\&quot;MsoNormal\\&quot;\"> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">9.&nbsp;提供广阔的成长晋升空间、量身定制的多通道职业规划；</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span> </p> <p class=\"\\&quot;MsoNormal\\&quot;\"> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">10.&nbsp;薪酬组成：基本薪酬+项目奖金+年终奖金；</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span> </p> <p class=\"\\&quot;MsoNormal\\&quot;\"> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\">11.心有灵犀特色福利：免费咖啡+活泼舒适的工作环境；</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span> </p> <p class=\"\\&quot;MsoNormal\\&quot;\"> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span> </p> <p class=\"\\&quot;MsoNormal\\&quot;\"> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span> </p> <p class=\"\\&quot;MsoNormal\\&quot;\"> <span style=\"font-family:宋体;color:#282828;font-size:10.5pt;\"></span> </p>
